      <body>
         <div type="edition">
            <ab> 
               <lb n="1"/>
                  <persName>
                     <name key="Eutyches Εὐτύχηϛ">Εὐτύχηϛ</name>
                  </persName>καρύδαϛ
               <lb n="2"/>
                  <persName>
                     <name type="divine" key="Hekate Ἑκάτη">Ἑκάτῃ</name>
                  </persName> εἰϛ τὰ πάτη
               <lb n="3"/>ἀναφορὰν ἀνέθηκεν.
            </ab>
         </div>
         <div type="translation">
            <p>Eutyches, the walnut dealer, gave (this) as an offering to Hekate for the pate.</p>
         </div>
         <div type="commentary">
            <p>Basis of verification: photo.</p>
